Mean GE over time is plotted for both conditions in Fig. 1. The difference in GE between conditions was 0.9% over the entire trial. From minute 5–8, the N − H difference was 0.6% ± 0.7%, from minute 15–18, the difference was 1.1 ± 1.3%, both significant. No significant change in GE within trials was observed comparing GE over the first half (min 5–8) with GE over the second half (min 15–18).Fig. 1
